.I ethX

.B ethtool \-r|\-\-negotiate
.I ethX

.B ethtool \-S|\-\-statistics
.I ethX

.B ethtool \-t|\-\-test
.I ethX
.B1 offline online

.B ethtool \-s
.I ethX
.BI speed \ N
.B2 duplex half full
.B4 port tp aui bnc mii fibre
.B2 autoneg on off
.RB [ advertise
.IR N ]
.RB [ phyad
.IR N ]
